{"tid":1668731,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《小丑》預計收78億元","createTime":"2019-10-22T07:05:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T07:17:12.000Z","uid":19552,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2d8e2a55ea26f6968208b85c2d5795471cc48e31","tid":1668731,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T07:05:21.000Z","msg":"由祖昆馮力士（Joaquin Phoenix）主演的《JOKER小丑》（Joker）創下票房神話，上映三周票房已成為限制級（R-Rated）影史上第四位，直逼《死侍》（Deadpool）於2016年大收7.83億美元（約61億港元）之紀錄。業內人士估計，《JOKER小丑》最終會大收10億美元（約78億港元），成為DC史上最賣座作品。而安琪蓮娜祖莉（Angelina Jolie）主演之《黑魔后2》（Maleficent: Mistress of Evil）於北美開畫成績卻未如理想，比上一集首周票房幾乎少一半。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191022/large/1571663980_2082.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191022%2Flarge%2F1571663980_2082.jpg&h=64fccf41&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7d82877cf7858342813713bcec84584220ac7e93","tid":1668731,"uid":265168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T07:17:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">快推行動po<br />\n推到有人搞</span></span><br />\n開咗兩個po都仲未上到熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n快啲一齊討論！<br />\n<br />\n[擴大戰線]  [行動] 與其嘈加泰集會 不如唔搞呢個<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1668190\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1668190</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}